      "content": "it's just weird cuz when i look at the transfer volumes and the way specific sectors are being drained right before the quarterly reports, it looks so calculated. like, it isn't just market fluctuation, it looks like a deliberate restructuring. if i'm right, and this is some kind of controlled transition, what kind of role do you think someone in my position actually plays? like, am i just a cog, or am i seeing the architecture of it all?",
